description:
Celebrate your passion for PAC-MAN's Pals with these cosmetic items as you eat to compete!

This PAC includes:
- 1 Fyger (body)
- 1 The Prince (body)
- 1 Pooka’s Goggles (face)
- 1 Pooka’s Goggles - Rare (face)
- 1 Klonoa (head)
- 1 Dig Dug Helmet (head)
- 1 Dig Dug (maze)
- 1 Mr. Driller (maze)
- 1 Galaga (maze)
- 1 PAC-MAN 3D (icon)
- 1 Inky 3D (icon)
- 1 Blinky 3D (icon)
- 1 Pinky 3D (icon)
- 1 Clyde 3D (icon)
- 1 Frightened Ghost 3D (icon)
name: PAC-MAN Mega Tunnel Battle: Chomp Champs - Namco Pals PAC
